Build nmapsi4 on GNU/Linux

Required:
* qt4
* cmake >= 2.6
* nmap >= 5.51 with nping for discovery tool

Recommend:
* dig package (debian: dnsutils)

Build:

# cd tools/
# ./cmake_verbose_script.sh
cd ../build/
# make
# make install (only root) || download or create a package for your disto ;)

For the Packages:
http://www.nmapsi4.org


The nmapsi4-admin.desktop used kdesu by default or is possible:

* change Exec=nmapsi4 with Exec=kdesu/su-to-root nmapsi4

__________________________________________________________________________________

MS Windows:
for build nmapsi4 on MS windows visit: http://www.nmapsi4.org

Mac Os:
for build nmapsi4 on Max Osx read: http://www.nmapsi4.org/node/38

